# ML Training Pipeline (Airflow + MLflow + Postgres)

## What it does
- Loads Boston Housing dataset
- Stores in Postgres with deduplication
- Trains Ridge and XGBoost with hyperparameter tuning
- Tracks experiments with MLflow
- Selects best model based on RMSE
- Stores metrics in database

## Tech stack
- Airflow
- MLflow
- PostgreSQL
- scikit-learn
- XGBoost

## How to run
- Requires Airflow + Postgres + MLflow running